{"tid":2339785,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加強反共實力，台灣24年來首次擴增軍隊","createTime":"2020-12-25T02:38:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T23:55:22.000Z","uid":337052,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"661d51aa6bb7bc08df3df200839ba18c62c687da","tid":2339785,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:38:21.000Z","msg":"【獨家】守護台灣！國防部明年元旦新編2個旅 2023年再增3個旅<br />\n22小時前<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/gzODy7xxkxVhlE45PKrhBY0emWM=/760x427/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JRJBPWLMKBADTFPPRDV66LEJCY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgzODy7xxkxVhlE45PKrhBY0emWM%3D%2F760x427%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJRJBPWLMKBADTFPPRDV66LEJCY.jpg&h=30c71848&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國防部明年擴編2個步兵旅，至2023年將增編5個旅。資料照片<br />\n<br />\n中共解放軍威脅台灣國防安全日趨嚴重，國防部為此專案報請總統蔡英文核定，<span class=\"red\">2021年元旦在北部地區擴編第109步兵旅及南部地區擴編第117步兵旅。國防部將領並向《蘋果新聞網》證實，未來將繼續依期程新編北、中、南部地區3個步兵旅，預計在2023年12月31日全數編成。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">這也是自1997年李登輝執政期間開始執行的國軍精實案，迄今24年後，首度在蔡英文任內進行擴編。</span>另外，由於美方今年同意出售岸置魚叉飛彈，作為台灣「岸防巡航飛彈系統」（CDCM，Coastal Defense Cruise Missile），並搭配國軍現在擴編的岸置型雄二、雄三反艦飛彈，<span class=\"red\">因此目前擁有7個岸置雄風飛彈中隊的海鋒大隊，將會大幅擴編，未來主官也將由上校升格為少將。</span><br />\n<br />\n將領指出，因應中共解放軍的敵情威脅，國防部依據「提升後備戰力」專案規劃期程，將國軍現有7個步兵旅的戰力進行國土防衛外，目前已奉核再編成5個步兵旅，<span class=\"red\">總計共有12個第一類型「灘岸守備旅」，以強化第一線灘岸守備戰力。</span>而目前已完成各項整備工作，明年1月1日即可依計畫於北部及南部地區各擴編1個步兵旅。<br />\n<br />\n至於明年1月1日編成的2個步兵旅，據了解，在北部的步兵旅則是以陸軍「北區專長訓練中心」為主體編成陸軍第六軍團第109步兵旅；另外「南區專長訓練中心」則編成陸軍第八軍團第117步兵旅，這2個步兵旅的編制均為「五個步兵營，再加一個砲兵營」。將領表示，這2個擴編的步兵旅，平時擔任新兵訓練任務，而在戰時則擔任國防防衛戰中的灘岸守備旅任務。（王烱華／台北報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20201224/FN2KXHWYNZBGBEEBE6GBAODLR4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20201224%2FFN2KXHWYNZBGBEEBE6GBAODLR4%2F&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGtwx%2F1T5MpBrdTD4T%2Fai5QWg%3D&h=9dde7842\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20201224%2FFN2KXHWYNZBGBEEBE6GBAODLR4%2F&h=75f8c98b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20201224/FN2KXHWYNZBGBEEBE6GBAODLR4/</a>"},{"pid":"5e6be611011fc4ad81096be12a0c6803a841bdf6","tid":2339785,"uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:43:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Rxo0XmNYTCYcf4YuFEz1cA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3MS4y/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/tFCIGnCzniOg81WDeX9FbQ--~B/aD0zNTc7dz02MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/youthdailynews_517/80ea4c3dabf4005d4bc50e7638a4017c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FRxo0XmNYTCYcf4YuFEz1cA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3MS4y%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FtFCIGnCzniOg81WDeX9FbQ--~B%2FaD0zNTc7dz02MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fyouthdailynews_517%2F80ea4c3dabf4005d4bc50e7638a4017c&h=6d60941c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n裝甲542旅聯兵1營戰1連戰車排輪訓。（542旅提供）<br />\n<br />\n台灣進行聯兵旅改革"},{"pid":"4e403c3810efa2852f223bb10bceb69788a8e6f3","tid":2339785,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:45:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.upmedia.mg/upload/content/20201216/Gc201216140703747563.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fupload%2Fcontent%2F20201216%2FGc201216140703747563.jpg&h=a7efd711&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upmedia.mg/upload/article/20201216141124140525.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fupload%2Farticle%2F20201216141124140525.jpg&h=98720a4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聯兵旅加強實地訓練"},{"pid":"0a43c8b9ca11fcbc4058c81b108ac1e4b36967cd","tid":2339785,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:48:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">中科院今起試射飛彈 共艦提前現蹤</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n2020/12/24 05:30<br />\n〔記者涂鉅旻、陳賢義／綜合報導〕<span class=\"red\">中科院今日起在台東外海規劃「火砲試射」，根據其彈道高度「無限高」及廣大的危險海域推測，應為防空飛彈射擊演訓。</span>不過，中國一艘軍艦前天晚上在我國東部廿四浬臨接區以外出沒，直至昨日清晨才脫離，活動時間雖和國軍演訓期程未重疊，但我方仍提高警覺監控。國軍強調，對於周遭海空域動態皆能充分掌握、應處。<br />\n<br />\n根據漁業署「射擊通報」揭示資訊，<span class=\"red\">中科院訂定在本月廿四日、廿五日、廿八日、廿九日於台東外海進行「火砲試射」，其危險區域延伸至綠島、蘭嶼以北及以東海、空域，彈道高度為「無限高」，研判應為天弓二型、三型飛彈、愛國者二型飛彈等防空彈種射擊測試或訓練。</span><br />\n<br />\n另外，中科院表定本月廿九日至卅一日於同一區域進行彈道高度二萬五千呎（約七六二○公尺）的「火砲試射」演訓。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，中國一艘軍艦自前天晚上在蘭嶼南方海域出沒，並一路向南航行，昨日清晨脫離我國監控範圍。由於該艦未進入廿四浬臨接區海域，海軍無法驅趕，僅能監控其動態。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/paper/1421038\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fpaper%2F1421038&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGtwx%2F1T5MpBrdTD4T%2Fai5QWg%3D&h=e53259d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fpaper%2F1421038&h=932826a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/paper/1421038</a>"},{"pid":"724fef2cfcd722cb4cf49e1e3668a1c0e15d8181","tid":2339785,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:54:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgcdn.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/1024/20201223/2000x1121_0980061867956.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgcdn.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F1024%2F20201223%2F2000x1121_0980061867956.jpg&h=5c6114c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n空軍防空部射擊天弓三型防空飛彈。（國防部提供）"},{"pid":"82c2519bd92043a72be845ea1b155fbf3a989e78","tid":2339785,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:55:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsimg.ftv.com.tw/summernotefiles/News/4c18c506-ed88-4a02-aae5-3fd756fecd98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsimg.ftv.com.tw%2Fsummernotefiles%2FNews%2F4c18c506-ed88-4a02-aae5-3fd756fecd98.jpg&h=25f9a6c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a51f405e2994de9f6a688985aee73890142d5f5","tid":2339785,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:56:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.ftvnews.com.tw/manasystem/FileData/News/9ee83f57-6638-4926-a68d-2f2607f61837.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.ftvnews.com.tw%2Fmanasystem%2FFileData%2FNews%2F9ee83f57-6638-4926-a68d-2f2607f61837.jpg&h=8230c5f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中科院從今晚開始一連四天在台東外海試射「無限高」火炮，外界研判是天弓和愛國者等型飛彈。"},{"pid":"e117180f27ecde7eab980127d05715dc4bbf98e8","tid":2339785,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"661d51aa6bb7bc08df3df200839ba18c62c687da","tid":2339785,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:38:21.000Z","msg":"【獨家】守護台灣！國防部明年元旦新編2個旅 2023年再增3個旅<br />\n22小時前<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/gzODy7xxkxVhlE45PKrhBY0emWM=/760x427/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JRJBPWLMKBADTFPPRDV66LEJCY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgzODy7xxkxVhlE45PKrhBY0emWM%3D%2F760x427%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJRJBPWLMKBADTFPPRDV66LEJCY.jpg&h=30c71848&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國防部明年擴編2個步兵旅，至2023年將增編5個旅。資料照片<br />\n<br />\n中共解放軍威脅台灣國防安全日趨嚴重，國防部為此專案報請總統蔡英文核定，<span class=\"red\">2021年元旦在北部地區擴編第109步兵旅及南部地區擴編第117步兵旅。國防部將領並向《蘋果新聞網》證實，未來將繼續依期程新編北、中、南部地區3個步兵旅，預計在2023年12月31日全數編成。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">這也是自1997年李登輝執政期間開始執行的國軍精實案，迄今24年後，首度在蔡英文任內進行擴編。</span>另外，由於美方今年同意出售岸置魚叉飛彈，作為台灣「岸防巡航飛彈系統」（CDCM，Coastal Defense Cruise Missile），並搭配國軍現在擴編的岸置型雄二、雄三反艦飛彈，<span class=\"red\">因此目前擁有7個岸置雄風飛彈中隊的海鋒大隊，將會大幅擴編，未來主官也將由上校升格為少將。</span><br />\n<br />\n將領指出，因應中共解放軍的敵情威脅，國防部依據「提升後備戰力」專案規劃期程，將國軍現有7個步兵旅的戰力進行國土防衛外，目前已奉核再編成5個步兵旅，<span class=\"red\">總計共有12個第一類型「灘岸守備旅」，以強化第一線灘岸守備戰力。</span>而目前已完成各項整備工作，明年1月1日即可依計畫於北部及南部地區各擴編1個步兵旅。<br />\n<br />\n至於明年1月1日編成的2個步兵旅，據了解，在北部的步兵旅則是以陸軍「北區專長訓練中心」為主體編成陸軍第六軍團第109步兵旅；另外「南區專長訓練中心」則編成陸軍第八軍團第117步兵旅，這2個步兵旅的編制均為「五個步兵營，再加一個砲兵營」。將領表示，這2個擴編的步兵旅，平時擔任新兵訓練任務，而在戰時則擔任國防防衛戰中的灘岸守備旅任務。（王烱華／台北報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20201224/FN2KXHWYNZBGBEEBE6GBAODLR4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20201224%2FFN2KXHWYNZBGBEEBE6GBAODLR4%2F&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGtwx%2F1T5MpBrdTD4T%2Fai5QWg%3D&h=9dde7842\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20201224%2FFN2KXHWYNZBGBEEBE6GBAODLR4%2F&h=75f8c98b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20201224/FN2KXHWYNZBGBEEBE6GBAODLR4/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T03:27:57.000Z","msg":"台軍好似將各市後備指揮部常備化，宣布總動員令後即時就地征照到數十萬後備軍(7年內退役兵)"},{"pid":"a23f594efa4ee75f023bf05fb2ed3b845b449cad","tid":2339785,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e117180f27ecde7eab980127d05715dc4bbf98e8","tid":2339785,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"661d51aa6bb7bc08df3df200839ba18c62c687da","tid":2339785,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:38:21.000Z","msg":"【獨家】守護台灣！國防部明年元旦新編2個旅 2023年再增3個旅<br />\n22小時前<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/gzODy7xxkxVhlE45PKrhBY0emWM=/760x427/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JRJBPWLMKBADTFPPRDV66LEJCY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgzODy7xxkxVhlE45PKrhBY0emWM%3D%2F760x427%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJRJBPWLMKBADTFPPRDV66LEJCY.jpg&h=30c71848&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國防部明年擴編2個步兵旅，至2023年將增編5個旅。資料照片<br />\n<br />\n中共解放軍威脅台灣國防安全日趨嚴重，國防部為此專案報請總統蔡英文核定，<span class=\"red\">2021年元旦在北部地區擴編第109步兵旅