n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20201224/FN2KXHWYNZBGBEEBE6GBAODLR4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20201224%2FFN2KXHWYNZBGBEEBE6GBAODLR4%2F&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGtwx%2F1T5MpBrdTD4T%2Fai5QWg%3D&h=9dde7842\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20201224%2FFN2KXHWYNZBGBEEBE6GBAODLR4%2F&h=75f8c98b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20201224/FN2KXHWYNZBGBEEBE6GBAODLR4/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T03:27:57.000Z","msg":"台軍好似將各市後備指揮部常備化，宣布總動員令後即時就地征照到數十萬後備軍(7年內退役兵)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T03:31:02.000Z","msg":"教召每年增至26萬人 嚴德發：將成立防衛動員署<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgcdn.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/1024/20201007/1152x768_771115600654.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgcdn.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F1024%2F20201007%2F1152x768_771115600654.jpg&h=4916a220&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202010070041.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202010070041.aspx&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGtwx%2F1T5MpBrdTD4T%2Fai5QWg%3D&h=de477ccd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202010070041.aspx</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T03:44:29.000Z","msg":"全民防衞變成一盤生意<br />\n<br />\n依靠軍工出口可內循環增就業率"},{"pid":"7924302646bec3936155ffb30d701c9434b67d55","tid":2339785,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e94c97dbc60b9c70fa62370d1be2b9568742f634","tid":2339785,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a23f594efa4ee75f023bf05fb2ed3b845b449cad","tid":2339785,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e117180f27ecde7eab980127d05715dc4bbf98e8","tid":2339785,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T03:27:57.000Z","msg":"台軍好似將各市後備指揮部常備化，宣布總動員令後即時就地征照到數十萬後備軍(7年內退役兵